South African singer Lethabo Sebetso, aka Focalistic, has promised to buy award-winning superstar singer, Davido, a Rolls Royce when he’s rich enough. “ When I get rich, I am buying you another Rolls,” Focalistic said in a line from his appreciation message to Davido. Focalistic, a former football player turned singer, sent an appreciation message to Davido for the success of their collaboration, Champion Sound. “Big Bro, I just want to say thank (you) for taking a chance with me!! I’ll always appreciate what you’re (you have) done for me!! Love you forever!!”   Why crime is high among youths – M.I Abaga     Only women can brag about s3x- Okon Lagos     I lost self-confidence after scarred face – Sonia Ogiri   - Advertisement - Responding to Focalistic’s message, Davido simply thanked him for sharing his sound and talent with him. “Thank you for sharing your sound with me,” Davido responded. ‘Champion Sound,’ a song by Davido featuring Focalistic was released in 2021 and was premiered on YouTube on November 19, 2021. The song has a total of 11,916,651 views and has further skyrocketed Focalistic’s career. SPONSORED